Startup scripts are launched from /etc/rc.local

omxplayer is a modified version that allows looping.

Network interfaces are setup in /etc/network/interfaces

Screen blanking time is set in /etc/kbd/config (BLANK_TIME).
Screen blanking is used to hide the console on the main terminal when videos are playing.

To power off the screen:
$ tvservice -o

To power on the screen:
$ tvservice -p && fbset -xres 1872 -yres 1031 && fbset -xres 1872 -yres 1032 
